I truly love this game! Characters were a delight to talk to and get to know(Oh Silas<3), even tho the map is a bit of a maze heheh

My only wish is that it was waaayyy longer, I NEED a second game to know how it will go with Tulio & SIlas!!! ;v; And more lore & magpies!!! I LOVED IT, good world building with notes throughout dialogue so you dont feel dogpiled with history! 

And ofc the graphics were stunning, my only problem was a light/shader glitch I got where the light didn't pass through correctly, or it went straight through walls... And if I stood a specific place it worked correclty, it was weird.. ^^;
